6
One Move Captures Black (11)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par
\par If this shape appeared in a real game, it might have become a pae.
\par
\par It is easy to make a pae.
\par It is hard to capture black unconditionally. If you know a lot of proverbs, you can solve this problem in no time.
\par }
