Diagram 1 (Most Common)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's cut at W1 is the most common move.
\par
\par Black plays dansu at 2 making a pae.
\par Anyone can read this much.
\par
\par It is, however, brilliant when you capture this group unconditionally. Where's the vital point?
\par }
