Diagram 4 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\fbidis\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\ltrpar\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Do you remember the proverb which states, "play at the center of three stones?"
\par
\par Following this proverb,  white's placement at 1 is the center of three stones. If black plays at 2, white's cut at 3 is severe. Black cannot play dansu from either direction.
\par
\par
\par }
