Diagram 5 (Variation)
[{\rtf1\fbidis\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\ltrpar\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If black responds to \'a1\'e2 at 1, white 2 is a good move.
\par Black has no response.
\par
\par The most frequently occurring vital point in the corner is the 2-1 point but please do not forget that the center of three stones ican also be a vital point.
\par
\par
\par }
